quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  51,31,"Annabi Ibraahiima maaki Malaa'i…ďe …ďen : ko hon…óum woni fii mon? E ko faanditi…óon?"
  51,32,"Malaa'ika'en jaabii mo wonnde : menen, Allah neli men e yim…ďe bom…ďe …ďen faggitotoo…ďe kuu…óe bon…óe."
  51,33,"Fii yo men accitu e ma…ď…ďe, kaa∆īe iw…óe e loope ju…óaa…óe"
  51,34,"Maandiniraa…óe ka Joomi maa an Ibraahiima, wurtaa…óe e yawtoo…ďe keeri Allah …ďen, fantinoo…ďe yeddugol Mo ngol."
  51,35,"Men yaltini taho kala gom…óim…ďe wonunoo…ďe e saare yim…ďe Luutu …ďen, fii wata lepte bom…ďe …ďen hawru e ma…ď…ďe."
  51,36,"Men tawaano e nden saare, si wanaa suudu juul…ďe wooturu, ndun le ko suudu …ďeynguure Luutu nden (yo o his)."
  51,37,"men acci e nden saare yim…ďe Luutu, batteeji lepte …óen, ko holla wonnde …óe yanuno e ma…ď…ďe, wona waajitor…óum kala huloowo lepte muusu…óe …óen yanunoo…óe e ma…ď…ďe, ontigi hula wa…óugol sugu kuu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen, fii da…óugol …óen lepte."
  51,38,"Men acci kadi maande e Muusaa, tuma nde Men nulunoo mo e Fir'awna, wonndude e hujjaaji …ďanngu…ói, wonannde kala huloowo e lepte muusu…óe …óen."
  51,39,"Kono Fir'awna …óuurni fawaade e cemmbe e konu makko fow salii goonga, o wi'i Muusaa : ko mbil…óotoo…óo yim…ďe maa hara feetu…óo."
  51,40,"Men nanngi mo kanko e koneeli makko …óin fow, Men weddii …ďe ka maayo, …ďe yoolii …ďe halkii, tawde Fir'awna ko feliraa…óo fennugol mo ngol nodditoo rewetee…óo."
  51,41,"Men acci kadi maande e 'Adi'en, yim…ďe Huudu …ďen, wonannde kala huloowo lepte muusu…óe …óen, tuma nde Men wurtunoo e ma…ď…ďe henndu ndu ardaa e to…ďo, ndu worgintaa le…ó…óe ndu aldaa kadi e barke."
  51,42,"Ndu accataa hay wonkii maa jawdi ekw e kon ko ndu arani, si wanaa ndu muncay fii mun, ndu wa…óta …óum wano rappunde sariinde."
  51,43,"Men wa…ói kadi maande e Samuuda'en, yim…ďe Annabi Saalih …ďen, wonannde kala huloowo lepte muusu…óe …óen, tuma nde …ďe wi'ananoo : awa dakmitoree nguurndam mon …óam, ado lajal mon gal timmude."
  51,44,"∆Āe townitanii yawmiroore Joomi ma…ď…ďe gom…óingol e …óoftagol Mo ngol, haacaango lepte ngon nanngi …ďe, tawi hi…ďe ∆īeewa ko …óum jippotoo kon. Tawde …ďe kammbirano lepte …óen, bal…óe tati ado …óe jippaade."
  51,45,"∆Āe waawaano du√Īugol lepte …óen gaay e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe he…ďaano kadi feere faabeede."
  51,46,"Gom…óii kadi Men halkiriino yim…ďe Nuuhu …ďen ado …ďee jantaa…ďe …óoo, yoolagol. Pellet, …ďen ko yim…ďe yaltunoo…ďe e …óoftaare Allah, wa…ói si …ďe hanndi e lepte Makko …óen."
  51,47,"Kammu ngun, Men mahir ngu doole Amen, Men …óiggini …óum. Pellet, ko Men yaanoo…ďe cebe mammba."
  51,48,"Leydi ndin kan, Men weertiranndi ho…óoo…ďe …ďen, wano nda…ó…óundi ma…ď…ďe. Men mo∆ī∆īii weertan …ďe ndi."
  51,49,"E kala huunde, Men tagii noone …ói…ói: wano deyel e gorel, kammu e leydi, njodrndi e maayo; balajo'o on waajitoray gootaagu Allah tagu…óo …óin On, tesko…óon fii kattal Makko ngal."
  51,50,"Dogee lepte Allah …óen, yaccoron e mbarjaari Makko ndin, …óoftaare e anngal yeddugol Mo. Min, wonannde on onon …ďee yim…ďe, ko mi jertinoowo e lepte Makko …óen, …ďanngu…óo jertinol."
  51,51,"Wata on wa…óde e Allah rewetee…óo goo ko rewon. Min, wonannde on immorde ka Makko, ko mi …ďanngu…óo jertinol."